## 🚀 **Setup Instructions**

### **Step 1: Create Project**

```bash

npx create-react-app vyoma-portfolio

cd vyoma-portfolio

```

### **Step 2: Install Dependencies**

```bash

npm install @fontsource/tenor-sans @fontsource/montserrat lucide-react

```

### **Step 3: Setup Tailwind CSS**

```bash

npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer

npx tailwindcss init -p

```

### **Step 4: Configure tailwind.config.js**

```javascript

/** @type {import('tailwindcss').Config} */

module.exports = {

content: [

"./src/**/*.{js,jsx,ts,tsx}",

],

theme: {

extend: {},

},

plugins: [],

}

```

### **Step 5: Replace Files**

Replace all the files in your src directory with the provided code above.

### **Step 6: Run the Project**

```bash

npm start

```

## 📝 **Key Features Included**

✅ **Responsive Design** - Works on all devices

✅ **Dark Theme** - Modern dark UI with teal/blue accents

✅ **Smooth Animations** - Hover effects and transitions

✅ **Modern Typography** - Tenor Sans + Montserrat fonts

✅ **Interactive Navigation** - Sticky header with scroll tracking

✅ **Tech Stack Icons** - Visual tech skills representation

✅ **Project Filtering** - Filter projects by status

✅ **Social Links** - LinkedIn, GitHub, Email integration

✅ **SEO Ready** - Semantic HTML structure

✅ **Performance Optimized** - Clean, efficient code

## 📞 **Customization Notes**

1. **Update Personal Info**: 




🚀 Setup Instructions
Step 1: Create Project
npx create-react-app vyoma-portfolio
cd vyoma-portfolio
Step 2: Install Dependencies
npm install @fontsource/tenor-sans @fontsource/montserrat lucide-react
npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer gh-pages
npx tailwindcss init -p
Step 3: Replace ALL Files
Replace all the above files in their respective locations.

Step 4: Update package.json homepage
Change YOUR_USERNAME to your actual GitHub username in package.json

Step 5: Run Locally
npm start
Step 6: Deploy to GitHub Pages
git init
git add .
git commit -m "Initial commit"
git remote add origin https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/vyoma-portfolio.git
git push -u origin main
npm run deploy
🎉 Your portfolio will be live at: https://YOUR_USERNAME.github.io/vyoma-portfolio

